## The goal of this task to create a script to secure copy file from local to remote machine

## Step 1
## Check environmental variable for REMOTE_USER and REMOTE_IP
## IF iether environmental variable is missing, ask the user for the issing variable.

## Step 2
## Script must take positional variable as file to copy 
## IF postional param is missing, ask the user manually

## Step 3 
## Use the gathered data to transfer file from local to remote server under /tmp/ directory

## Step 4 
## Notify the user the job is completed. 

